Rating: 3
I didn't have smoked haddock. I used fresh haddock and added a bit of liquid smoke to the poaching liquid. I also added a bit of paprika and carrots. served it with crusty sourdough bread, rather than the crackers. It was delicious. I will make it again.

Rating: 3
This chowder is delicious, would give it 3 1/2 forks if I could. Certainly would not serve 6 as a main course however - 3 or 4 max.